Global burden of gout in 1990-2019: A systematic analysis of the Global Burden 
of Disease study 2019.

Jeong YJ(1), Park S(1), Yon DK(2), Lee SW(3), Tizaoui K(4), Koyanagi A(5)(6)(7), 
Jacob L(5)(8), Kostev K(9), Dragioti E(10), Radua J(11)(12)(13)(14), Stickley 
